{
  "id": "s1-01",
  "title": "시대별 유물/유적지",
  "era": "삼국",
  "eraLabel": "고대/중세 (삼국·남북국)",
  "sectionId": "s1",
  "content": "<details><summary><strong>🗺️ 시대별 유물/유적지 요약노트</strong></summary><div class=\"content\">\n\n  <details class=\"sub-details\"><summary><strong>🪨 구석기 시대</strong></summary><div class=\"content\">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>구분</th>\n          <th>내용</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>사회</td>\n          <td><span class=\"highlight\">무리사회</span> (무리지어 이동), <span class=\"highlight\">평등한 사회</span> (배고픈 평등)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>식생활</td>\n          <td>채집, 수렵 (사냥)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>의생활</td>\n          <td>가죽옷 (수렵 후 걸치는 정도)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주거</td>\n          <td><span class=\"highlight\">이동 생활</span> → <span class=\"keyword\">동굴</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">막집</span> (대충 막을 쳐서 만든 집)</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>유물</th>\n          <th>유적지</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">뗀석기</span> (돌과 돌을 부딪혀 만든 도구)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>└ <span class=\"keyword\">주먹도끼</span> (대표적인 뗀석기)</td>\n          <td>경기 <span class=\"keyword\">연천 전곡리</span> (주먹도끼 발견)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td></td>\n          <td>충남 <span class=\"keyword\">공주 석장리</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td></td>\n          <td>단양 금굴 (동굴 주거)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td></td>\n          <td>청원 두루봉 동굴 (흥수아이 뼈 발견 논란)</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div></details>\n\n  <details class=\"sub-details\"><summary><strong>🌱 신석기 시대</strong></summary><div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"note\">⚡ <span class=\"highlight\">농경의 시작</span>과 함께 <span class=\"highlight\">정착생활</span>이 시작된 <span class=\"highlight\">신석기 혁명</span>의 시기!</div>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>구분</th>\n          <th>내용</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>사회</td>\n          <td>씨족사회, 부족사회 (혈연으로 연결된 무리)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>식생활</td>\n          <td>채집, 수렵 + <span class=\"highlight\">농경 시작</span> (반농사: 씨를 뿌려 거두는 정도)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>의생활</td>\n          <td>옷감 제작 시작</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>주거</td>\n          <td><span class=\"highlight\">정착생활 시작</span> → <span class=\"keyword\">움집</span> (강가/바닷가, 반지하 형태, 가운데 화덕)</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>유물</th>\n          <th>유적지</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">간석기</span> (돌을 갈아 만든 매끈한 도구)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>└ 갈돌 (농경 도구)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">가락바퀴</span> (실을 감는 도구)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">뼈바늘</span> (옷감 제작 도구)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">토기</span> (농작물 저장용)</td>\n          <td></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>└ <span class=\"keyword\">빗살무늬 토기</span> (대표적인 토기)</td>\n          <td>서울 <span class=\"keyword\">암사동</span> (대표적 신석기 유적지)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">패총</span> (조개무덤, 조개 쓰레기장)</td>\n          <td>부산 <span class=\"keyword\">동삼동</span> (패총 발견)</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div></details>\n\n  <details class=\"sub-details\"><summary><strong>🔑 시험 핵심 키워드</strong></summary><div class=\"content\">\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>시대</th>\n          <th>키워드</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>구석기</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">막집</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">동굴</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">뗀석기</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">주먹도끼</span></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>신석기</td>\n          <td><span class=\"keyword\">가락바퀴</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">빗살무늬 토기</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">움집</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">뼈바늘</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">농경</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">토기</span></td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div></details>\n\n</div></details>",
